{"tid":1790778,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【經濟客飯】邱騰華真儍定扮蠢？ - 曾國平","createTime":"2019-12-20T09:00:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T10:43:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d3c6fbcb1f8f0bb9b5b0a07104129a2fc511594b","tid":1790778,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T09:00:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20191220/20828409\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191220%2F20828409&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5QDpGYGFnKQRHckm7FIFNPY%3D&h=0e22552c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191220%2F20828409&h=bdc0e14d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20191220/20828409</a><br />\n<br />\n【經濟客飯】邱騰華真儍定扮蠢？ - 曾國平<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191220/large/1576772287_93fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191220%2Flarge%2F1576772287_93fb.jpg&h=2c7d96ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n越多人討論黃色經濟圈，越多人提出歪理謬論，例如日前商經局局長邱騰華跟網民「對話」（哲學問題：你可以跟錄音機對話嗎？），指香港經濟結構從來不單一，以黃藍政治立場區分，或以某類特定先決條件去決定光顧哪類店舖，並非港人信奉原則，「全世界都冇人劃地為牢，睇唔到呢樣嘢可以點持續落去」。這個經濟零分（政治也不見得高分）的答案，竟出自一位管轄香港商務及經濟發展的高官之口，真係唔知點反應好。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">沒特定先決條件去消費的，肯定是奇人異士。難道局長會合埋雙眼隨機決定去邊度食飯？</span>商戶為利益驅使，真黃扮黃各出其謀吸客，點樣同自由經濟有衝突？我不知局長真儍定扮蠢，只知類似言論會以不同形式不斷出現。為大家免受荼毒，我提供一段簡單易明的「黃色經濟圈簡述」，藉以對抗愚昧：「黃色經濟圈係一個經濟現象，唔需要乜『大台』中央集權。就好似有人鍾意買有機產品，有人堅持飲公平貿易咖啡，有人鍾意少油少糖。黃色政見係個人喜好，有需求就有供應。商戶為消費者提供黃色消費體驗，亦係自由經濟運作下結果。喜好有代價，黃色要求太高就難免賣得貴，但市場會搵到均衡點，畀消費者去滿足唔同程度嘅黃色生活。撐黃拒藍嘅港人越多，越多黃店生存，就係咁！」<br />\n<br />\n曾國平<br />\n美國維珍尼亞理工大學經濟系副教授<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/economics3.0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Feconomics3.0%2F&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5QDpGYGFnKQRHckm7FIFNPY%3D&h=1668fb15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/economics3.0/</a><br />\n本欄逢周五刊出<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2a0baf62e2cdc61f89d273b102c33b392ffa1a9","tid":1790778,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T09:02:52.000Z","msg":"20 DEC 2019 星期五 <br />\n全民口罩日<br />\n<br />\n今晚<br />\n時間：8:00pm開始<br />\n【和你撐手足】荔枝角聲援手足集會<br />\n地點：荔枝角收押所外（九龍蝴蝶谷道5號）<br />\n⭐️已批不反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日期:2019年12月21日(星期六)<br />\n時間:下午1時至5時<br />\n杜絕政治酬庸<br />\n銀髮族集會<br />\n地點:愛丁堡廣場大會堂對出空地<br />\n不反對通知書申請中<br />\nfacebook銀髮族老而不廢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n12.21 元朗見<br />\nSat 15:00 YOHO MALL<br />\n毋忘721恐襲<br />\nRemembering 721 Terror<br />\n<br />\n通告 Notice<br />\n如元朗党鉄站提早至下午關閉,<br />\n活動將於下列商場繼續:<br />\n屯門   V city<br />\n沙田  連城廣場<br />\n荃灣  荃灣廣場<br />\n將軍澳 Popcorn<br />\n中環  ifc mall<br />\n元朗 YOНО MALL"},{"pid":"ca532ca7656d4e09b3187d0a9fca643bcb6dbb3d","tid":1790778,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T09:03:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5QDpGYGFnKQRHckm7FIFNPY%3D&h=589fc314\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetow